**See also:** [GE-20260524-c1e573](GE-20260524-c1e573.md) — quarkus.arc.exclude-types silently fails for beans registered by a Quarkus extension

**See also:** [GE-20260601-cee623](GE-20260601-cee623.md) — QuarkusTestProfile.getEnabledAlternatives() replaces selected-alternatives entirely

